        "username": "Brent_S",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/brent_s/{size}/3332_2.png",
        "created_at": "2021-12-31T01:05:08.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Congrats on getting the Presle and Boloree. Those are hard to come by. And pricey.</p>\n<p>Reviews-William Kelly is more upbeat then Galoni. These will be great wines but probably off on quality from the last few vintages, but time will tell.</p>",
